description: This dashboard will be used to test the production tracker. Please set the date you view the site, also what the url of the site you are testing.
title: Production Tracker Testing

dashboard_elements.body_text:
This is where to view the data for the production tracker testing. Select the date you did the testing, also what the page url is. The page url filter is set to 'contains' because if you are testing a wide range of pages like gov, or a exact url. 

The node id  is only on the Main Gov site, but it is important to know if it is being collected.
dashboard_elements.body_text_as_html:
This is where to view the data for the production tracker testing. Select the date you did the testing, also what the page url is. The page url filter is set to ‘contains’ because if you are testing a wide range of pages like gov, or a exact url.

The node id is only on the Main Gov site, but it is important to know if it is being collected.
